Package org.loboevolution.js

Interface Window

All Superinterfaces:
AbstractView, EventTarget, GlobalEventHandlers, WindowBase64, WindowConsole, WindowEventHandlers, WindowOrWorkerGlobalScope, WindowTimers
All Known Subinterfaces:
WindowProxy
All Known Implementing Classes:
WindowImpl
public interface Window extends EventTarget, GlobalEventHandlers, WindowBase64, WindowConsole, WindowEventHandlers, WindowOrWorkerGlobalScope, WindowTimers, AbstractView
A window containing a DOM document; the document property points to the DOM document loaded in that window.
